This paper presents a novel approach for computing knowledge graph embeddings, which is a popular topic in the field of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The approach is evaluated on two datasets, DrugBank and DBpedia, which are commonly used in the field of databases (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the task of type prediction, which is relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and semantic web (cs.SI).
